1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,119
The jailer is passed out drunk.

3
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,119
Hurry up and talk.

4
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:42,039
In a short while,
I'll come and take you away.

5
00:00:46,119 --> 00:00:46,920
Mr. Liu.

6
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,880
Are you okay?

7
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:50,439
Your hand!

8
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:51,240
It's nothing.

9
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,960
I've had way worse injuries
as a constable.

10
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,679
Wu Lian is such a despicable coward.

11
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:57,719
I got you into this mess.

12
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:58,880
It's no big deal at all.

13
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:03,320
Leave Nanny He's matter to me.

14
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,400
I'm no longer a constable,

15
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,640
but I still have a few

16
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,560
trusted friends in the County Office.

17
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,640
Don't worry.

18
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:09,959
Everything will be fine.

19
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,079
Thank you so much, Mr. Liu.

20
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,359
Go now.

21
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,599
Take good care of yourself.

22
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,719
You too.

23
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:26,820
=Episode 4=

24
00:01:28,159 --> 00:01:29,400
(Grind Hard, Go Far)
The Princess Consort orders:

25
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,200
(Grind Hard, Go Far)
Wu Lian spread malicious rumors.

26
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,719
Kneel and embroider robes
for Lady Cheng'en.

27
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:36,159
Until Her Ladyship is fully appeased.

28
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:39,799
(300 taels of silver)
Nanny, why punish me at midnight?

29
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,200
Nanny He did the inspection.

30
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,799
Lady Cheng'en is a virgin.

31
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,920
Wu Xin.

32
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,319
This Nanny He...

33
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,480
Understood.

34
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,400
Master.

35
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,400
As you commanded,

36
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,480
I didn't actually inspect her.

37
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:04,120
I just lied that she was a virgin.

38
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,359
Well done.

39
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,039
Nanny He, won't this offend

40
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,000
the Princess Consort?

41
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,599
If it weren't for you, Master,

42
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,560
I'd be dead on the streets by now.

43
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:19,000
I'd lay down my life for you forever.

44
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,159
Thank you, Master.

45
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,560
Please punish me, Your Honor.

46
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,280
I locked you up to keep you

47
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:42,000
out of the chaos outside.

48
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,719
You were reckless enough

49
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,879
to break out of jail.

50
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,520
It was an emergency.

51
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,960
I accept your punishment.

52
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:52,039
I know you're a man of principle.

53
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,319
For that girl's sake,

54
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,439
jail can never hold you.

55
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,599
You need to leave

56
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:00,400
this cursed Jinxiu City.

57
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,560
Go! Hurry up and go!

58
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,400
Your Honor.

59
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,599
You know everything, don't you?

60
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,719
Know what?

61
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,439
I know absolutely nothing.

62
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,800
The manor inspected Lin Rulan
last night,

63
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,960
only confirming she's the real Lady.

64
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,560
If the Princess Consort finds out,

65
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:37,159
do you know the penalty
for slandering a Lady?

66
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,800
Please give me one more chance, Master!

67
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,199
Speak.

68
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:46,680
I have someone to kill her for us.

69
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,080
He has no ties to the embroidery house.

70
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:53,120
We won't be implicated even if we fail.

71
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:57,599
It's Jia Yi, Lin Rulan's ex-fiancé.

72
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,680
He led the mob that drove her to death.

73
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:04,479
He's terrified of her ghost the most.

74
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,680
How did it go?

75
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,879
I scared the living daylights
out of him.

76
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,800
He should be here any minute now.

77
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,399
Thank you for your hard work, Priest.

78
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:18,800
Thank you, Ms. Meng.

79
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,199
If you breathe a word of this,

80
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,160
you'll be banished from Jinxiu City.

81
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,959
I take money

82
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,879
to solve people's problems.

83
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,079
I won't say a single word.

84
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,360
Then please go inside

85
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,319
and prepare for tomorrow's ritual.

86
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,120
Ms. Meng!

87
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,319
Ms. Meng!

88
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,199
Ms. Meng!

89
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,079
Please save me!

90
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,759
What's wrong, Mr. Jia?

91
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:42,000
Save me, Ms. Meng!

92
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,959
The priest said...

93
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,519
He said

94
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,959
Lin Rulan's ghost is back!

95
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:46,399
She's coming for my life!

96
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,560
You were her fiancé.

97
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:52,199
You led the mob
that drove her to suicide.

98
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,120
If she's coming for you,

99
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,680
what does that have to do with us?

100
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,319
I...

101
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,920
Three years ago,

102
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:03,360
your Master made me marry Lin Rulan.

103
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:05,120
But she refused,

104
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,000
so your Master

105
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,199
ordered me to drive her to suicide.

106
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,199
If I hadn't taken the blame,

107
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,759
I wouldn't be in this mess!

108
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,959
Jia Yi, don't forget,

109
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,680
you profited a lot

110
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,279
from what happened back then.

111
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,160
Fine.

112
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,480
I'll let you stay
at the embroidery house.

113
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,079
But you must do exactly as I say.

114
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,319
Stick close to me,

115
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,600
and I'll keep you safe.

116
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,600
That's perfect!

117
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:31,279
To be with a beauty like you...

118
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,120
Don't act so innocent.

119
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:38,439
You and Lin Rulan

120
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:40,360
are just your Master's bed warmers.

121
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,720
Watch your stitching.

122
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,160
Yes, I know.

123
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,959
Master.

124
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,959
Jia Yi has arrived.

125
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,680
When will it be done?

126
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,680
Tomorrow.

127
00:05:57,940 --> 00:06:00,600
(Evil purged, Wu Xin killed Nanny He)

128
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,800
(Evil purged, Wu Xin killed Nanny He)
Nanny He is dead.

129
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,480
Wu Lian has another blood on his hands.

130
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:08,959
Xiaojiu.

131
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,959
Tomorrow...

132
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,439
Let go of all attachments.

133
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,519
Enter the afterlife.

134
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,480
Wandering spirits, depart!

135
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,360
Enter reincarnation!

136
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,279
Wandering spirits, depart!

137
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:28,720
Enter reincarnation!

138
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,959
What if the grievance remains?

139
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:37,199
So you're alive, not a ghost.

140
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,319
Thank you for your hard work, Priest.

141
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,720
Rulan.

142
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:54,959
Does it hurt?

143
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:58,199
This place is long abandoned.

144
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,519
You can speak freely now.

145
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:04,759
Rulan, how did you come back to life?

146
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,959
This is your old family home, right?

147
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,959
You must have moved to a big mansion.

148
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,600
How many dirty deeds have you done
for Wu Lian?

149
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,680
How many embroiderers' virtue

150
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,800
did you destroy for wealth and power?

151
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:21,600
They may be noble-born,

152
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,920
but they're just ordinary women.

153
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,720
Using their virtue to inspire the Master

154
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:29,000
to create peerless embroidery

155
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,560
is his greatest gift to them.

156
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,519
If not for the Master's skills,

157
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,600
their virtue would be worthless.

158
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:40,759
You really are his most loyal dog.

159
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,720
You've said so much

160
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:45,079
just to figure out my plan,

161
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,720
so your Master can decide

162
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,959
how to kill me,

163
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:49,800
right?

164
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,720
Rulan.

165
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,079
We're like sisters.

166
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,759
How could you think that of me?

167
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,079
Sisters?

168
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,040
We stopped being sisters
three years ago.

169
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:03,120
You stopped me from reporting him
to the government office.

170
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:05,199
Do you think I'd trust you now?

171
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,120
But things are different now.

172
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,600
I've been by the Master's side
for years,

173
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,000
and I finally understand.

174
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:13,920
He's like the bright moon,

175
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,120
high above us all.

176
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:18,720
Serving him is our greatest blessing.

177
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,600
What blessing did Xiaoyi get?

178
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,480
Xiaoyi was our friend.

179
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,959
You just watched Wu Lian bully her!

180
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,079
If she'd been obedient,

181
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:27,519
she wouldn't have ended up like that.

182
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:29,439
I'm here to convince you

183
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,480
to work for him.

184
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,480
You could be

185
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,879
second only to him in Jinxiu City.

186
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,519
Isn't that good?

187
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,519
Why must you oppose him?

188
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:38,399
He took my virginity three years ago.

189
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,600
He tried to kill me.

190
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,360
If I let him go now,

191
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,720
I'd betray the girl I was
three years ago.

192
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,519
You're utterly stubborn!

193
00:08:57,799 --> 00:09:01,000
So I didn't
just have Jia Yi trick you here.

194
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,639
I also sent for your parents.

195
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,159
You ungrateful brat!

196
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,960
Why didn't you just stay dead?

197
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,120
You've shamed us completely!

198
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,159
Rulan, you're tainted now.

199
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,519
You can't live like this.

200
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,279
Save me!

201
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,519
I want to live!

202
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,759
Want them to live?

203
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,000
Get in there.

204
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:29,799
Get in!

205
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,480
Rulan!

206
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:00,360
Rulan.

207
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:03,039
For the sake of our sisterhood,

208
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:05,080
I'll give you a quick death.

209
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:06,960
Jia Yi.

210
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,720
Rulan!

211
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:16,480
Die in there!

212
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:19,519
Or the Lin family will never know peace!

213
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,720
Ms. Meng.

214
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,000
We did as you asked.

215
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,360
Rulan went inside.

216
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,159
Now keep your promise.

217
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,039
Our payment...

218
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,759
Thank you, Ms. Meng.

219
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,440
What are you looking at?

220
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,159
Go on! Get out of here!

221
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,360
Hurry up! Leave!

222
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,320
Go! Go!

223
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,720
Father.

224
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:47,960
Mother.

225
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,320
Nothing has changed at all.

226
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,360
Rulan.

227
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,159
For the Lin family's honor,

228
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,360
die here in peace.

229
00:10:59,279 --> 00:11:01,080
I'll give you a proper burial.

230
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:04,960
Better than being a wandering ghost.

231
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,679
Father.

232
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:08,000
Mother.

233
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:14,720
From now on, I disown you both.

234
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:49,580
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

235
00:11:49,820 --> 00:11:52,820
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

236
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:56,780
♪The past no longer binds♪

237
00:11:57,260 --> 00:12:00,980
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

238
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:05,540
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

239
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:09,260
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

240
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:11,620
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

241
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:15,700
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

242
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:18,300
♪For your faith that never broke♪

243
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:22,620
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

244
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,420
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

245
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:29,660
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

246
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:33,340
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

247
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:36,100
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

248
00:12:36,100 --> 00:12:38,700
♪One thought turns into ash♪

249
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:45,020
♪No future left to write♪

250
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,900
♪If I never fall♪

251
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:50,300
♪How could this waiting end♪

252
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,660
♪If I bear no scars♪

253
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:53,980
♪How could I challenge fate♪

254
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:56,340
♪I knew there was no way back♪

255
00:12:56,340 --> 00:13:00,340
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

256
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:02,580
♪For your faith that never broke♪

257
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:06,740
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

258
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:09,620
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

259
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:14,020
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

260
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:17,700
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

261
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:20,300
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

262
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:22,660
♪One thought turns into ash♪

263
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:29,020
♪No future left to write♪

264
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:32,300
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

265
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:35,700
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

266
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:39,580
♪If we meet again someday♪

267
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:45,820
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
